& [InferenceJobResult] is boundary delineation proposal
  + [focus] is the primary subject of attention
  + [inside] is the scope explicitly covered by this job
  + [boundary] separates what is in scope from out-of-scope content
  + [outside] includes any material not relevant to the current inference
  + [inference] is the conclusion drawn about delineation boundaries
  + [caution] reminds that no repo changes are made here
  + [next_step] is to hand off this proposal for review
